Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama! Taru-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, I appreciate that you invited me\N to come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Mimora like mountains too? \NMe love mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If it lets me spend time with Taru-sama like this, \NI absolutely
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,lo-AUGHHHHHHH-ve mountain climbing! {no clue what's the joke here}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. The air is so clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it feels good to be one with nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we've come, Korekiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rightly so, Jabao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you say bounces back at you! {/voice}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called a mountain echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain Echo must be awfully busy all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Taru-chan, what we call a mountain echo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when you make a sound here, \Nand then it bounces off the mountains back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Mountain Echo-san \Ndoesn't need to answer to every single sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mountain Echo, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Taru's voice returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain Echo's an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me if you disagree! {no clue why he says "talk back if you're frustrated (over a failure, humiliation or injustice); annoyed; chagrined; (bitterly) disappointed; bitter; vexed; frustrating; annoying; regrettable"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See? He's right there. {no clue what he means by "properly exists, assumed "told  you, there is someone"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.
