Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone! For how much longer will we have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? {no clue why'd he say yes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's lunch time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Honmaru, we're eating bento?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey-hey, do you suggest we eat \Nin the middle of this road?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear with it for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Bento, bento!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, if we walk for a little longer, \Nwe'll arrive to a beautiful lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Bento! Bento! Bento!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey-hey, yo-yo-yo. \NIf that's where we're having it, let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, let's hurry up. {no idea what to make of zen}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Bento! Bento!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...Bento! By the lake! \NMe and Honmaru are having a bento! We'll eat a ben... {mostly a guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, this is highly improper of you. {improper; immodest; disgraceful; shameful; vulgar; low}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what about that meal...? \NLet's eat already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lake looks sad. {tlc, no clue what's this last word, assumed some corrupted form of kitanai, though I suspect "kawaisou"}{5:53: I'm hearing "湖悲しそう"\NA loose TL would be something like "The lake looks sad"\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Come eat bento with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bento!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, you're such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's luxurious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope everyone finds it to their taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, it's absolutely delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, I wonder what Iyona-chan's taste like. {no clue, could be "which ones are ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you! What the hell do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, please try the bento I made too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delicious, Iyona!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You goddamn bet it was! {not sure what he mean}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell did you gobble it all up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. Look, I got more of it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Would've been better if you said so earlier! {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, you wouldn't give my bento \Nso much as a glance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the final straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened to Taruruuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan, where's Taruruuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mimora-chan got mad \Nand sent him away! {/hid him somewhere} {not sure this is kakurechatta but I don't see other options, no clue what he means, where she hid him or what;}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So even you can't stand Taruruuto sometimes, Mimora-chan? {very unsure, I suspect ".... doesn't care for ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,By my word, I will never forgive Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan, if you don't mind, \Ncould you please share with us the bento you made?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Most certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch-ouch-ouch. Mimora suddenly goes mad, \Nme don't understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You! {g, probs hora}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? {g, prolly doushio}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You were making a fool of me earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Me was making a fool of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Making a fool! Making a fool! Making a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Me join you too! {tlc, only hear "ore mo nakama ni *** morau zo", no clue what he means}{Aurelius: 10:10: I'm hearing "俺も仲間に入れてもらうぞ"\NA loose TL would be something like "I'll join you guys too!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosesu-su-su!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! He's gathering empty cans! {hope it's akikan, no clue what's iro in the end though}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A good guy. I like that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For how long do you plan to hide Taru-chan from us? \NDon't you think it'd be better for him to show up soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But for sure, you do seem to eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is still growing, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I think, I'll go with Mimora-chan and look for Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll join you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean... There's no need, you can just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Mimora-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I said! I'm still not done with my meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan, how far did you send Taru flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't finished eating yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't find him soon, \Neveryone will get suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me. \NPerhaps, it's about time I forgave him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do it in an inconspicuous way. {/in a way that [magic] is not leaked/exposed}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Taru-sama, say "aah."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They've made up that soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, here, say "aah."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Iyona-chan would do something like that for me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,With this idiot in the way, there's not a chance of it happening.{assumed he refers to jabao, though could be rui or even everyone present}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd sure be nice if he disappeared off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Honmaru? \NIs there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a weird fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, boy am I thirsty!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, time to empty one more. {no clue what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, the juice you drink in the mountains is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Jabao threw away a can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Threw away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I said this because I do have a problem with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's telling you not to litter in the nature. {actually "don't throw away garbage on earth/ground and trees" but that's kinda cryptic especially in egnlish}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not buying that childish crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what everyone else does!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't throw away empty cans here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You again! {very unsure it's anta}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem, you ass?! {unsure what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem, you ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop mimicking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop mimicking me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimicking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimicking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Me - Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, I'm Mimora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm Mountain Echo Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Taro! Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the mountain echo who said "I'm not an idiot?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say? I'm not an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Honmaru being an idiot is a confirmed fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were mistaken on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No I wasn't! You're all idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Throwing cans away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't throw away a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is the one who did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You also littered here earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I've seen it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? When did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take our litter home, so forgive us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no business apologizing to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not the only ones who come here \Nto litter away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:06.96,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5203AE&\xshad-6\yshad2\4c&H7C3D12&\bord1}Yahoo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan got turned into a crystal ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, this must be voice magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Mountain Echo Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Return them to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan apologized, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't care. Not listening to what idiots say. {first word is yadabe - I think a variation of "yada"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You prick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain Echo Taro, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop admiring him! Do something about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Mountain Echo Taro used voice magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use voice magic too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:05.94,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H9B8644&\3c&H27A5B4&}Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You showed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Showed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Showed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Showed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.95,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5D11B4&\3c&H884D12&}Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,About time I dealt with you as well! {おまえもたまにしてやる - unsure what means}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5B0BB3&\3c&H864B09&}Yahoo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, you can just dodge it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll chase you forever! {no clue what he says, translating line from manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a nice weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weakness is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No-no-no-no, stop it please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to stop, \Nreturn everyone back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, Mimora-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, stop the bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Me like Mountain Echo Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountain Echo Taro can't stand the sound of empty cans. {no clue what means}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Me get rid of empty cans - \Nbecome friends with Mountain Echo Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You... I sent you flying, you not mad at me?{not sure what to make of yatsuketa}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there! You're getting a little too close, you two! {/don't hug too much}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Litter of the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there really this much litter, \Neven on a mountain that looked so clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But Taru, how do you intend to bring it with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I'm the Great Magician. \NI'll use Sword-Pen Magic-kun. {no clue why he uses sword and not board pen for drawing, was this way in manga as well}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your trouble. \NI'll return everyone back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was wondering if I could ask for one more favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Speak your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thing is, it's about...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what just happened to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I still feel some emptiness in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a dream. A dream. You were seeing a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Were we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Taru and Mimora-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right. They returned home already.  {/went ahead}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! A giant monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I do like me a trip to civilization every now and then! {guess, assumed "hito to kaeru mitakatta ze" but doesn't make sense, TLC}{22:10: I'm hearing "おら一度都会を見たかったべ"\NA loose TL would be something like "I've always wanted to see the city"\NYamabiki Taro is a country bumpkin so you can get a little creative with his lines if you want.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Mountain Echo Taro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Taru-sama, the ten minutes are almost up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru? Honmaru, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna take Iyona-chan out on a date in the park, \Namidst the falling leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.29,0:22:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru always so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:22:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll help in any way I can!
